5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

port-type

Generic function

Summary

Returns the type of the specified port.

Signature

port-type port => type

Arguments

port
An instance of type <port>.

Values

type
An instance of type <symbol>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the type of port.

See also

port-modifier-state, page 331

port-name, page 332

port-pointer, page 333
